#: ../../spinningup/exercises.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Instructions.** Write a function that takes in the means and log stds "
"of a batch of diagonal Gaussian distributions, along with (previously-"
"generated) samples from those distributions, and returns the log "
"likelihoods of those samples. (In the Tensorflow version, you will write "
"a function that creates computation graph operations to do this; in the "
"PyTorch version, you will directly operate on given Tensors.)"
msgstr ""
"**說明。** 撰寫一個函式，輸入一批對角高斯分佈 (Diagonal Gaussian Distribution) "
"的均值和對數標準差，以及（先前產生的）這些分佈的樣本，並回傳這些樣本的"
"對數似然值。（在 Tensorflow 版本中，你將撰寫一個建立計算圖運算的函式來完成此操作；"
"在 PyTorch 版本中，你將直接對給定的 Tensor 進行操作。）"

#: ../../spinningup/exercises.rst:29
msgid ""
