#: ../../spinningup/exercises.rst:56
msgid ""
"**Evaluation Criteria.** Your solution will be evaluated by running for "
"20 epochs in the InvertedPendulum-v2 Gym environment, and this should "
"take in the ballpark of 3-5 minutes (depending on your machine, and other"
" processes you are running in the background). The bar for success is "
"reaching an average score of over 500 in the last 5 epochs, or getting to"
" a score of 1000 (the maximum possible score) in the last 5 epochs."
msgstr ""
"**評估標準。** 你的解答將在 InvertedPendulum-v2 Gym 環境中執行 20 個訓練週期 "
"(Epoch) 來評估，這大約需要 3-5 分鐘（取決於你的機器以及背景中正在執行的"
"其他程序）。成功的標準是在最後 5 個訓練週期中達到平均分數超過 500，或在"
"最後 5 個訓練週期中達到 1000 分（最高可能分數）。"

