#: ../../spinningup/exercises.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Evaluation Criteria.** Evaluate your code by running ``exercise1_3.py``"
" with HalfCheetah-v2, InvertedPendulum-v2, and one other Gym MuJoCo "
"environment of your choosing (set via the ``--env`` flag). It is set up "
"to use smaller neural networks (hidden sizes [128,128]) than typical for "
"TD3, with a maximum episode length of 150, and to run for only 10 epochs."
" The goal is to see significant learning progress relatively quickly (in "
"terms of wall clock time). Experiments will likely take on the order of "
"~10 minutes."
msgstr ""
"**評估標準。** 透過在 HalfCheetah-v2、InvertedPendulum-v2 以及你選擇的另一個 "
"Gym MuJoCo 環境（透過 ``--env`` 旗標設定）中執行 ``exercise1_3.py`` 來評估"
"你的程式碼。該設定使用比典型 TD3 更小的神經網路（隱藏層大小 [128,128]），"
"最大回合長度為 150，且僅執行 10 個訓練週期。目標是在相對較短的時間內"
"（以實際時間計）看到顯著的學習進展。實驗大約需要 ~10 分鐘。"

#: ../../spinningup/exercises.rst:83
msgid ""
"Use the ``--use_soln`` flag to run Spinning Up's TD3 instead of your "
"implementation. Anecdotally, within 10 epochs, the score in HalfCheetah "
"should go over 300, and the score in InvertedPendulum should max out at "
"150."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``--use_soln`` 旗標可以執行 Spinning Up 的 TD3 而非你的實作。"
"根據經驗，在 10 個訓練週期內，HalfCheetah 的分數應該超過 300，"
"InvertedPendulum 的分數應該達到最高的 150。"

